nodes.title: About Krit
nodes.info:
Krit is currently partaking his senior year studies in Computer Science at Mahidol University International College, a field of study that has fascinated him ever since when he was young.

During his free time, Krit is an avid gamer, as well as an anime enthusiast. He also occasionally partakes in cross country running and other activities such as biking.

Outside of his studies, Krit is a down-to-earth volunteer who loves giving back to the community around him. His most notable volunteering job is Tournament Coordinator for the naval-based video game World of Warships, where he has been actively volunteering for the job since 2018.
